  "observations": [
    "Bookings list partitioned by tabs (Upcoming/Past/Pending/Cancelled) ג€” status-driven feed partitioning",
    "Event Types presented as card-feed with per-type inline configuration entry",
    "Availability uses multi-schedule model (working/on-call/vacation) with per-event-type schedule binding",
    "Event Type config is deep nested form with sections Basic/Advanced/Apps/Workflows/Limits",
    "Booking questions authored as form-builder ג€” user constructs schema declaratively",
    "Round-robin configured as sub-section with algorithm picker (load-balanced/optimal/custom)",
    "App Store as marketplace feed with install/uninstall plugin lifecycle and per-app config screens",
    "Routing forms with conditional rules map answers ג†’ host ג€” pre-booking routing layer before slot picker",
    "Booker view embeddable as iframe/popup/inline ג€” embed is first-class distribution surface",
    "Slot picker auto-detects booker timezone with manual override",
    "Host-moderated confirmation flow: booking starts in pending, host confirms or rejects",
    "Insights dashboard per team/member with funnel metrics (visitג†’slotג†’bookג†’attend) and rate statistics",
    "Teams nested inside organizations with collective (multi-host) event-types",
    "Developer API key management as separate section with scoped credentials and last-used tracking",
    "Workflows declarative ג€” trigger + action list (SMS/email/webhook) bound to event-types via join entity"
  ]
